ygData.messageBody:
In the water there somewhere in Dagnor's is the entrance to another dungeon
called "Kedge Keep" the entire dungeon is underwater and the entrance is
guarded by two lvl 35+ swordfish, and it gets worse from there on in. Not
much more info but hopefully a little more than ye knew b4!

Quindinar
